Grover's Search Algorithm and Amplitude Amplification
=====================================================

Overview
--------

Quantum search algorithm and more via amplitude amplification.
:math:`\ket{x}\bra{x}`
 
.. math::

    V_n = \sum_{j=1}^{m} \beta_{jn} A_j  \qquad \qquad n=1, 2, \dots , n_s


      l
